# Plan 5: Releases/Discography Section

## Goal
Create the "Music" page to display albums and singles, fetching data from the SQLite database.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create `app/music/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Create a `ReleaseCard` component to display album artwork and title.
- [ ] Fetch tracks from the database, grouped by album/single.
- [ ] Implement a grid layout for releases.
- [ ] Add a "Play" button on the card to start playing the album in the global player.
- [ ] Create a detailed view for releases (optional modal or expand-in-place) to show the tracklist.
